&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;For other select roles, Coinbase is piloting BrightHire, an AI interview intelligence platform, to transcribe and summarize interview notes, allowing our interviewers to fully focus on you as the candidate.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Depending on your role and stage in the application process, you will be informed of the specifics regarding which tool(s) will be used as part of the interview process.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
