&lt;h2&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Software Engineer on the Experimental Projects team, you&#39;ll be at the forefront of innovation at Stripe, turning promising ideas into tangible solutions that could shape the future of our platform. You&#39;ll have the autonomy to identify opportunities, rapidly build prototypes, and work directly with users to validate and iterate on your solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
