greenhouse-7418422.description:
&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Flexport:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Flexport, we believe global trade can move the human race forward. That’s why it’s our mission to make global commerce so easy there will be more of it. We’re shaping the future of a $10T industry with solutions powered by innovative technology and exceptional people. Today, companies of all sizes—from emerging brands to Fortune 500s—use Flexport technology to move more than $19B of merchandise across 112 countries a year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The recent global supply chain crisis has put Flexport center stage as we continue to play a pivotal role in how goods move around the world. We are proud to have the support of the best investors in the game who believe in our mission, solutions and people. Ready to tackle global challenges that impact business, society, and the environment? Come join us.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The opportunity:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexport is a platform for global trade in an industry that comprises 12% of the global GDP.&amp;nbsp; We are the first licensed freight forwarder and customs brokerage built around a modern tech stack.&amp;nbsp; We help the world&#39;s fastest-growing brands manage their international supply chains, providing a fully-managed service for moving products between any two places on the planet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exceptional software development is integral in allowing us to fulfill our mission of fixing the user experience in global trade. At Flexport you’ll develop products that are at the forefront of reshaping the entire logistics &amp;amp; supply chain industries. You’ll work alongside self-starters interested in solving real-world problems and streamlining the inefficiencies in the complex global trade industry. You’ll have the opportunity to reshape an industry by creating the new operating system for global trade.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Welcome to our Cost Capture Team! We specialize in developing innovative tools that revolutionize procurement cost tracking across Ocean, Air, and Trucking freight logistics - or end-to-end cost tracking. Our mission is to create cutting-edge technologies that ensure all procurement contracts are digitized, centrally available, and readily exposed to Flexport systems for optimized decision making - whether that be decisions regarding procurement benchmarking, fulfillment optimization, bill processing, P&amp;amp;L planning, etc. - we work across a host of internal teams as a platform team within Flexport.&amp;nbsp; Our team is dedicated to tackling complex logistical challenges by leveraging comprehensive data insights, AI solutions, and automation across Flexport’s tech stack.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A successful candidate will be comfortable working alongside engineering peers and partnering with product and business stakeholders to represent technical considerations for our products. While logistics experience is a plus, it is not a requirement. We value a willingness to learn and a passion for innovation. You&#39;ll have the opportunity to expand your knowledge, work with industry experts, and contribute to impactful projects that drive efficiency and reliability in air cargo transportation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;***This role is based in Bellevue, WA, and requires in-person attendance five times a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, test, deploy, and maintain systems that represent the real-world intricacies of logistics entities, such as packing lists, booking notifications, and routing guides.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to code reviews to maintain code quality, share knowledge, and learn from other team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with business partners and product managers to translate complex business problems into elegant technical solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build highly available, secure, and distributed systems within a microservices architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with peer teams on cross-team projects, building solutions that add new functionality to multiple Flexport systems.&lt;/li&gt;
