&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Affirm is reinventing credit to make it more honest and friendly, giving consumers the flexibility to buy now and pay later without any hidden fees or compounding interest.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
