&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qoxvz75zfxfz86zgwmhwz74zz65zjk8jz88zgz84zwz68zioz65zz65zz76zz81zbwf&quot;&gt;Clear communication skills and ability to collaborate with cross-functional partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
